<em>Note</em> that an order cannot be cancelled as long as a payment is pending. The expiry times for the different payment methods are determined by Mollie and can be found <a href="https://docs.mollie.com/payments/status-changes#expiry-times-per-payment-method" target="_blank" rel="noopener">on this page</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span>.</p>
